rows.name:
Well look who it is! You really saved
us a lot of work back there. Thanks
for helping out with the repairs!

rows.label: tlk4130012101_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh yeah, about those Tirkin.
They're helping out with guard
duty over on Rahim's tower.

rows.label: tlk4130012101_msg0003
rows.name:
You really taught them a lesson, but I
felt a bit sorry for them, so I offered
them the job. They're good birds.
